  <aspecttable>C&amp;O 1980</aspecttable>
  <name>1-3 Head Absolute High Signal R-YGR</name>
  <reference>As described in the 1980 version of the Chessie System Operating Rules "Signal Rules - 281-292".</reference>
  <description>Appearances for a double 1-3 lamp signal head mast with fixed red top head and without other badging</description>
  
